docs.summary:
Set of key-value pairs. Additional contact fields, referenced by key.  
 (For custom fields, see contacts-fields-api)  
 Common extended fields:  
 - contacts.displayByFirstName (String) (ReadOnly) display name starting with first name  
 - contacts.displayByLastName (String)  (ReadOnly) display name starting with last name  
 - invoices.vatId (String)  
 - members.membershipStatus (String) values: APPROVED, DENIED, PENDING, INACTIVE  
 - members.mobile (String) values: true, false  
 - ecom.numOfPurchases (Number) (ReadOnly) count of Wix Stores purchases  
 - ecom.totalSpentAmount (Number) (ReadOnly) total amount Wix Stores purchases  
 - ecom.totalSpentCurrency (String) (ReadOnly) currency code of Wix Stores purchases (ISO 4217 Currency code)  
 - emailSubscriptions.subscriptionStatus (String) (ReadOnly) values: SUBSCRIBED, UNSUBSCRIBED, NOT_SET, PENDING  
 - emailSubscriptions.deliveryStatus (String) (ReadOnly) values: VALID, BOUNCE, INVALID, INACTIVE   
 - emailSubscriptions.effectiveEmail (String) (ReadOnly)

members.name: key:value
members.doc: `key` of type string, `value` of type ref

members.name: extendedFields
members.doc:
Set of key-value pairs. Additional contact fields, referenced by key.  
 (For custom fields, see contacts-fields-api)  
 Common extended fields:  
 - contacts.displayByFirstName (String) (ReadOnly) display name starting with first name  
 - contacts.displayByLastName (String)  (ReadOnly) display name starting with last name  
 - invoices.vatId (String)  
 - members.membershipStatus (String) values: APPROVED, DENIED, PENDING, INACTIVE  
 - members.mobile (String) values: true, false  
 - ecom.numOfPurchases (Number) (ReadOnly) count of Wix Stores purchases  
 - ecom.totalSpentAmount (Number) (ReadOnly) total amount Wix Stores purchases  
 - ecom.totalSpentCurrency (String) (ReadOnly) currency code of Wix Stores purchases (ISO 4217 Currency code)  
 - emailSubscriptions.subscriptionStatus (String) (ReadOnly) values: SUBSCRIBED, UNSUBSCRIBED, NOT_SET, PENDING  
 - emailSubscriptions.deliveryStatus (String) (ReadOnly) values: VALID, BOUNCE, INVALID, INACTIVE   
 - emailSubscriptions.effectiveEmail (String) (ReadOnly)

members.name: locale
members.doc: Locale - IETF BCP 47 language tag (e.g., en-US).

members.name: primary
members.doc: Whether this is the contact's primary email. If no primary was defined, the first email address is primary by default.

members.name: e164Phone
members.doc: E164 Int'l phone number (this field is generated by phone and countryCode. If they don't fit to e164 format, an exception will be thrown).

members.name: primary
members.doc: Whether this is the contact's primary phone number. If no primary was defined, the first phone number is primary by default.

members.name: wixAppId
members.doc: Only returned for sourceType = WIX_*, i.e. for all Wix apps.

members.name: paths
members.doc: The set of field mask paths.

members.name: fields
members.doc: List of specific field names to return (if fieldsets are also specified, all requested fields will be included in the response).

members.name: fieldSet
members.doc: Controls which properties are returned. See [Fieldsets and Projected Fields](https://bo.wix.com/wix-docs/rest/crm/contacts/fieldsets-and-projected-fields).

docs.summary: will return error 403 INVALID_ARGUMENT if doesn't contain one of: name, emails, phones

members.name: allowDuplicates
members.doc: Whether to create a contact even when a contact with the same email address already exists. When false, and a contact with the same email exists, an error 409 FAILED_PRECONDITION (Duplicate) will be returned.

members.name: allowDuplicates
members.doc: Whether to create a contact even when a contact with the same email address already exists. When false, and a contact with the same email exists, an error 409 FAILED_PRECONDITION (Duplicate) will be returned.

members.name: fieldMask
members.doc:
Set of field paths to update. 
An empty field mask won't update the contact at all. An unknown field will return error 403 INVALID_ARGUMENT.
 add/remove array

members.name: revision
members.doc: Contact revision (Optmistic lock). When an old revision is passed, error 409 FAILED_PRECONDITION (Contact already changed) will be returned.

members.name: sourceContactIds
members.doc: Contacts to merge. Supports up to 5 contacts.

members.name: paging
members.doc: [Pagination](https://bo.wix.com/wix-docs/rest/crm/contacts/pagination), defaults to offset = 0 and limit = 50 (max limit 1,000).

members.name: fields
members.doc: The fields section is an array of field names returned

members.name: pagingMetadata
members.doc: Whether there are more pages but the site is to big to count, so the 'total' isn't available.

members.doc:
Override context, mandatory on server to server calls, requiring permission CONTACTS.ALLOCATE_ID
Optional on User identity
Forbidden on visitor/member identity

members.doc:
Indicates primary email is verified (first email on contact.emails)
manual verification

Indicates primary phone is verified (first phone on contact.phones)
manual verification

members.doc: explicit Contact ID.  must have "CONTACTS.MODIFY" on order to use this identifier
